data.description: ATTENTION - THIS IS AN ASSUMABLE MORTGAGE OPPORTUNITY AT 3.25%!! Spacious townhome in the desirable Sawgrass Subdivision of Crown Point! This spacious home offers over 2,000 SF of Luxury Living, featuring 9' Ceilings and all the comforts you would expect in a modern and maintenance free townhome! Offering -3- bedrooms, -2.5- bathrooms with an open concept main level featuring stainless steel appliances, quartz countertops and modern high-end cabinets. The primary bedroom is on the main level with exquisite en-suite, full bathroom with a luxury tiled shower and double vanity plus walk-in closet. Upstairs features two additional bedrooms with spacious closets and ceiling fans. Additional features include High-Efficiency Washer and Dryer, Economical Tankless Water Heater, Ultra-high Quality Marvin Windows, smart side composite siding and more! Terrific CENTRAL location -- just minutes away from the YMCA, schools, parks, golf course and downtown CROWN POINT! Ready for Immediate Occupancy!
